  <div>
    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">The Aberdeen Police Department is dedicated to protecting and serving the residents and visitors of Aberdeen through professional, community-oriented policing. The department employs <strong>45 sworn Law Enforcement Officers</strong> and <strong>17 civilians</strong>.</p>
    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Aberdeen is the largest municipality in Harford County, Maryland, located 26 miles northeast of Baltimore. The department is actively accepting applications for both <strong>Recruit</strong> and <strong>Lateral</strong> officers.</p>
